        <div class="experience-container">
            <h2>MY EXPERIENCE</h2>
            <div class="experience-timeline">
                <div class="experience-item">
                    <div class="experience-header">
                        <div>
                            <h3>Master's in Management</h3>
                            <p class="company">IE Business School, Madrid</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="timeline">2025 — Present</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="experience-description">Pursuing advanced business education while building expertise in digital marketing, entrepreneurship, and data-driven decision making. Applying academic knowledge to real-world SEO and web development projects.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="experience-item">
                    <div class="experience-header">
                        <div>
                            <h3>Freelance Web Developer & SEO Specialist</h3>
                            <p class="company">Self-Employed</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="timeline">2025 — Present</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="experience-description">Building conversion-focused websites and implementing local SEO strategies for small businesses. Specializing in dentists, spas, car care, and HVAC companies. Using modern tools like Claude Code, Cursor, Astro, React, and Tailwind to deliver fast, optimised websites that rank on Google and drive real business results.</p>
