                <div class="experience-item">
                    <div class="experience-header">
                        <div>
                            <h3>Venture Capital Analyst</h3>
                            <p class="company">Lisbon, Portugal</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="timeline">2023 — 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="experience-description">2 years of experience analysing tech startups, market trends, and investment opportunities. Developed strong analytical skills and understanding of what makes businesses succeed online—knowledge I now apply to helping small businesses grow through SEO and web development.</p>
